text: German Gazyumov (born 16 February 1936) is a Russian equestrian. He competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male equestrians Category:Soviet male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Soviet Union Category:Equestrians at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Moscow
